text: Fyodor Olegovich () was the Grand Prince of Ryazan (1427–1456) and son of Grand Prince Oleg II of Ryazan. ==References== Category:1360 births Category:1427 deaths Category:Grand Princes of Ryazan Category:Eastern Orthodox monarchs Category:14th-century monarchs in Europe Category:15th- century monarchs in Europe Category:Rurikids
